        <updateDate>2015-11-30T19:29:57Z</updateDate>
        <text><![CDATA[ <p>This bill prohibits federal funds from being obligated for the U.S. refugee admission of any alien: (1) whose country of nationality is Syria, Iraq, Libya, Afghanistan, or Yemen; or (2) in the case of an alien having no nationality, the country in which the alien last habitually resided is Syria, Iraq, Libya, Afghanistan, or Yemen.</p>]]></text>
      </summary>
    </summaries>
    <title>To prohibit obligation of Federal funds for admission of refugees from certain countries.</title>
